{"tid":1440544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好大獲 被抹黑 入黎睇下點拆","createTime":"2019-08-10T12:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T13:07:46.000Z","uid":288460,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d534cc314d65b8b0b86806eccd1d69e951aa138d","tid":1440544,"uid":288460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"今朝WHATSAPP收到一篇文 屌 好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 講到示威者係外國勢力, 打<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">經濟</span></strong>牌</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">轉載 :同美國政府熟嗰班美資基金第一季尾第二季頭已經開始狂沽港元,接到金管局手軟,手頭子彈由成二千億頂到得番五百億,仲少過之前想上市既百威啤酒一隻啤酒股集資既錢.跟住第二季開始大量沽空港元同港股.先用加中國關税,再喺香港攪反政府.同時攻擊股市同聯繫率,等港元一冧就平倉賺過百億.其實而家係打緊經濟戰,跟本唔須要出軍隊同飛彈.隊冧你國家政府,沽空你股市同貨幣,賺一大筆,就係嬴左你個國家.美國政府同特朗普有一大隊team日日夜夜博哂命去研究点整死中國,由台灣,中興,京東,華為到香港,招招都絕招.仲要可以令香港人自相殘殺.睇到香港啲新聞都不知幾開心,晚晚開香檳慶祝.同時啲港豬仲喺度破壞自己既地方同斷自己米路.嗰啲所謂香港人叻到呢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 屈人掉磚/圍POPO有錢收</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-510809750/1a-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-510809750%2F1a-1&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=7a32bd6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-510809750/1a-1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-510809750/2a-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-510809750%2F2a-1&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=c067b978\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-510809750/2a-1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 打家長牌 想令義士家人無BACKUP </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-510809750/whatsapp-audio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-510809750%2Fwhatsapp-audio&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=20f64b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-510809750/whatsapp-audio</a><br />\n<br />\n最近起緊大台 我極度懷疑係老共搞 分化成運動<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"f